    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Train Station Project》试玩版</strong>是一款让你扮演火车站经理的游戏。 从简单的任务开始，例如翻新和售票。 在完整版中，你还可以雇佣一支助理团队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>翻新</strong> – 清理破旧的车站大楼，清除堆积的垃圾，更换地板、粉刷墙壁并修理损坏的设备。 维护良好的建筑将吸引更多的顾客，并为你提供的服务带来更多收益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112070/extras/e42f3d9f549958bf6dff426fb1fd03a2.poster.avif?t=1756498030\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112070/extras/e42f3d9f549958bf6dff426fb1fd03a2.webm?t=1756498030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>服务顾客</strong> – 从售票开始，随着时间的推移逐步扩大提供的服务范围。 开设快递收发点和失物招领处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112070/extras/e6dd4f6b0cf428455f49e11540666b73.poster.avif?t=1756498030\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112070/extras/e6dd4f6b0cf428455f49e11540666b73.webm?t=1756498030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开设额外业务</strong> – 你的车站不仅仅是卖票！ 每次升级都会增加建筑的可用面积。 在完整版中，你可以开设自己的商店、安装自动售货机，甚至打造游戏厅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112070/extras/dc51d597099a4c38b6b93df6d0f9a2dc.poster.avif?t=1756498030\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112070/extras/dc51d597099a4c38b6b93df6d0f9a2dc.webm?t=1756498030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112070/extras/126ded5399f088001329b2d3d2937143.poster.avif?t=1756498030\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112070/extras/126ded5399f088001329b2d3d2937143.webm?t=1756498030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理</strong> – 请记住，你的资源并不是无限的。 你需要管理仓库，并定期为商店、自动售货机甚至办公室用品计划订货。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>火车！</strong> – 除了观察经过的客运列车外，你还可以通过为列车车厢进行清洁服务来赚取额外收入。 你可以跳过这些任务，但随着时间的推移，你将获得更重要职位的许可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112070/extras/454429e43d2dc6f4c3991996bfb7fe9a.poster.avif?t=1756498030\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112070/extras/454429e43d2dc6f4c3991996bfb7fe9a.webm?t=1756498030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关于试玩版</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此试玩版让你体验《Train Station Project》的核心管理和翻新功能，感受车站转型的开始。</p><br>车站大楼升级：可用至第 3 级（共 6 级）<br>洗手间升级：可用至第 3 级（共 6 级）<br>仓库升级：可用至第 1 级（共 4 级）<br>迷你超市、员工宿舍、游戏厅、照相亭和自助洗衣店：试玩版中锁定<br>所有主要建筑和自定义物品均可试用<br>活动和其他额外游戏系统受限<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：</strong> 员工宿舍、高级商店、娱乐室以及多个后期游戏功能仅在完整版中提供。</p>",
